    "description": "<p>CS Food started as a family business from the humble district of Geylang Serai in 1991. We specialise in the wholesale and retail distribution of beef, mutton, lamb and poultry. We have stayed true to our core values of Commitment and Sincerity throughout the years, maintaining a flexible approach that allows us to supply a wide variety of businesses, large and small, whilst offering the same trusted efficiency and affordable cost which has become synonymous with our name.</p>\n<p>In 2018, we set up a production facility to produce customised meat cuts and marination services, in addition to expanding a gourmet product line to meet market demands.</p>\n<p>Our continued growth and success is a result of the constant evolution and improvement of our services. we are characterised by our reliable, trusted service and extensive knowledge of the industry, and this is how we have gained and maintained our reputation.</p>",
